Automation Framework
-Java + selenium + TestNG + Maven + Page Object Model design pattern

1. Create a Maven project
   - Add all the dependencies in the pom.xml file
   
2. Create a folder structure
   - pageObjects
   - testbase
   - testcases
   - Utilities
   - logs
   - screenshots
   - reports
   - testdata
   
3. Create a Parent basePage with constructor under pageObjects package
   Create page object class for each webpage under pageObjects package which will extend basePage
   Create Accountregistration test case class under testcases packages
   Create randomStringUtils method to create random data for user registration
   Create a baseclass for reusable methods for all other test cases classes
   
4. Added log4j2.xml file in 
   